FuncDef: The display debugging etrunk command displays E-Trunk module functions, of which the debugging is enabled.

ParaDef.Info:
Specifies the ID of an E-Trunk.
The value is an integer ranging from 1 to 128.

Examples: [E-Trunk ID: 1] E-Trunk packet debugging switch is on
E-Trunk event debugging switch is on
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
To view E-Trunk module functions, of which the debugging is enabled, run the display debugging etrunk command.
